description: Folks, family, and friends of Folsom, you’re in for some frankly festive and fabulous times, all thanks to the crazy cool Kona Entertainment Vehicle (KEV) that’s bringing fluffy shaved ice, flowing flavors, and everything nice to your summer affairs, making them unforgettable!With the feel-good Calypso tunes and the famous Flavorwave that allows you to forge your own fruity formulas, Kona Ice of Folsom is the full monty when it comes to fun frozen treats!
name: Kona Ice of Folsom
